{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"array must conform to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"removeAnnotations:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1833"},"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotations:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotations:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"}}}